text: Sanne Verhagen (born August 24, 1992) is a Dutch judoka. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 57 kg event, in which she was eliminated in the second round by Dorjsürengiin Sumiyaa. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female judoka Category:Olympic judoka of the Netherlands Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:European Games competitors for the Netherlands Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games Category:Judoka at the 2019 European Games
